channel.title: I can't get onto my server
channel.description:
Okay, I just added color onto the skills of my server, but when I try to log on default 127.0.0.1 (pimpscape based), it won't let me in. Iv'e compiled, runserver, and everything. I even have voule's restarter fully working... It never did this to me before... Any ideas?
Then I downloaded a satan's isle to see if it would let me on there, and it did.
H E L P I S V E R Y M U C H A P P R E C I A T E D. :) `Play N Skillz`
